  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of the study is to characterize the epidemiologic data of the neonatal and infant
      cholestasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    recruitment difficulties
